   <p xml:id="46" begin="00:01:24.963" end="00:01:27.299">MY POINT WAS IF YOU CHANGE</p>
   <p xml:id="47" begin="00:01:25.964" end="00:01:28.534">IT FOR ONE GROUP, YOU HAVE</p>
